{#
    Shared admin layout chrome for the PPVenipak module.

    Required parameters:
      active_tab          — string identifier of the current tab
      page_title          — heading shown above the tabs
      page_description    — one-line explanation of what the admin does on this page

    Optional parameters:
      multistore_blocked  — when true, renders the multistore warning
      multistore_reason   — optional 'group' (default) or 'shared'. Switches the
                            warning copy between "pick a shop" and "switch to
                            All shops" depending on why the page is locked.
      page_actions        — pre-rendered HTML for the action button row (right-aligned)
#}

